@ptn・8 We’ve rolled out our update for miner asset class incentive split. As a reminder, we believe this will help to better balance the spread of information on our network, such that all asset subcategories will have at least some miners with high utility. There may be some odd behavior for the first month, as the market reorients itself towards the under appreciated assets.

